			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2184774">
									

<p>Alright. Thought I'd take advantage of the break and crank out another tale. This time around, I am finally introducing the very elusive Jericho T. Hill.</p>
<p>This is the third (and most likely final) installment in my series starring TwistedGears's Agent-Wizard: Daniel Navarro. If you haven't read them, the two previous installments can be found at <a href="/15-11-2012">15-11-2012</a> and <a href="/meeting-over-coffee">Meeting Over Coffee</a>.</p>
<p>Special thanks to djkaktus, TwistedGears, and Reach for looking this over and providing feedback on it when it was a mere draft.</p>
<p>Enjoy the tale. That is all.</p>

